@result
go-to: hartwig if (pro_republic / 3) > nationalism; hugenberg if (pro_republic / 3) < nationalism; westarp if ((pro_republic + nationalism) / 2) > 75

- @hartwig: Hartwig sweeps away the victory!
- @westarp: Westarp and Hergt barely scraped the stalemate for their benefit!
- @hugenberg: Hugenberg's radicals take over the party!

@hartwig
subtitle: Emil Hartwig gains the new ground!
on-arrival: dnvp_line = 1; dnvp_party_leader = "Emil Hartwig"; old_middle_dnvp -= 5; rural_dnvp -= 2; catholics_dnvp -= 1; new_middle_dnvp -= 2

= Emil Hartwig has secured the win in DNVP Congress of 1928!

Barely managing to secure the victory for the Christian - Socials / Young Conservatives / Green Front/ Landbund , Hartwig reorientates the party towards cooperation with Z, DVP, BVP and DDP to pressure them away from SPD, seeking to isolate SPD.

Enraged by the defeat, Hugenberg pulls out the media funding for the party and threatens to split away the party!

On the other ring, Lambach, Treviranus, Quaatz and Schiele are talking about how exactly should "constitutionalist - republican" DNVP look. Either case, it doesn't look like any development is beneficial for us.

@westarp
subtitle: Westarp regains the ground!
on-arrival: dnvp_line = 2; dnvp_party_leader = "Kuno von Westarp";

= Stagnating Stalemate of the DNVP 1928 Congress

Following the stagnation of the Congress votings, Westarp has stepped into it to secure former position once more, installing himself in the power! 

Christian Socials, Reich Landsbund (Rural League of the State) and Nationalists all have calmed down despite the blame shifting on Kuno Graf von Westarp on failures to unite the party under one wing.

@hugenberg
subtitle: Hugenberg carves up the old ways!
on-arrival: dnvp_line = 3; dnvp_party_leader = "Alfred Hugenberg"; new_middle_dnvp -= 5; old_middle_dnvp += 2; rural_dnvp -= 3; workers_dnvp -= 5

= Hugenberg takes the helm!

Following the empowerment of the Hugenberg, Hugenberg outs the Lambach and forces Westarp out of his position, fully consolidating the power for all-or-nothing radicals, ready to combat republican system once more...

Christian - Social DNVP deputies of the Reichstag begun mass attacks on the Hugenberg as uncompromissive and catastrophic for the stable electoral base of the DNVP! Remaining Landbund, Majority of Young Conservatives and Christian Socials seek to try to remove the Hugenberg and restore their power.
